5. Services Domain

services — id, key (fast_track, meet_and_greet, lounge_access), name, slug (unique), service_type, status, sort_order.
service_translations — id, service_id, locale, name, description, benefits, who_is_it_for, how_it_works. Unique (service_id, locale).
service_seo — id, service_id, locale, meta_title, meta_description, focus_keywords, canonical_url, og_image_key, schema_json, direct_answer_block, ai_summary. Unique (service_id, locale).

