6. Suppliers Domain

suppliers — id, name, legal_name, status (pending/verified/suspended), country_code, rating, reliability_score, payout_currency, payout_details (jsonb, encrypted at rest), created_by.
supplier_contacts — id, supplier_id, name, role, email, phone, whatsapp, is_primary.
supplier_airports — id, supplier_id, airport_id, status. Unique (supplier_id, airport_id).
supplier_services — id, supplier_id, service_id, status. Unique (supplier_id, service_id).
supplier_coverage — id, supplier_id, airport_service_id, status, priority. The precise "this supplier can fulfil this service at this airport" row, used by supplier assignment. Unique (supplier_id, airport_service_id).
supplier_documents — id, supplier_id, type (license/contract/insurance/other), storage_key (private bucket), status (pending/approved/rejected), expires_at, reviewed_by.
supplier_sla_metrics — id, supplier_id, period_start, period_end, response_time_avg_minutes, confirmation_speed_avg_minutes, cancellation_rate, no_show_rate, complaint_rate, reliability_score. Recomputed by a background job.

