8. Availability Domain

availability_rules — id, airport_service_id, days_of_week (int[]), time_windows (jsonb), cut_off_minutes, min_notice_minutes, capacity_per_slot (nullable), status.
supplier_schedules — id, supplier_id, airport_id, days_of_week, time_windows, capacity, status.
blackout_dates — id, scope_type (airport/airport_service/supplier), scope_id, date_from, date_to, reason.
capacity_rules — id, airport_service_id, slot_definition (jsonb), max_bookings.

Availability engine output is computed, not stored, except short-lived caching in Redis.

