9. Search Domain

Search in MVP runs on PostgreSQL full-text search over airports, airport_translations, services, and the airport_services join, filtered by availability and pricing at query time. No dedicated persistent search tables in MVP beyond:
search_synonyms — id, term, synonym (for IATA codes, city aliases, common misspellings).
Analytics of searches lives in the Analytics domain (search_events).

