12. Refunds Domain

refunds — id, booking_id, payment_id, type (full/partial/none), requested_amount_minor, approved_amount_minor, currency, reason, requested_by (customer/staff), policy_snapshot (jsonb — the cancellation policy as it was at request time), status (requested/admin_approved/finance_approved/processing/completed/rejected), admin_approved_by, finance_approved_by, stripe_refund_id, created_at, completed_at.
refund_status_history — id, refund_id, from_status, to_status, actor_id, note, created_at.
cancellation_policies — id, scope_type (airport_service/service/global), scope_id, windows (jsonb: time-before-service → refund %), supplier_penalty_rules (jsonb), status. The applicable policy is snapshotted onto the booking at booking time and onto the refund at request time.

