13. Incidents Domain

incidents — id, booking_id (nullable), supplier_id (nullable), type (flight_delay/supplier_no_show/passenger_no_show/wrong_terminal/communication_failure/payment_issue/service_complaint/other), severity (low/medium/high/critical), status (created/assigned/in_progress/waiting_external/resolved/closed), opened_by, resolution_reason, created_at, resolved_at.
incident_updates — id, incident_id, author_user_id, body, created_at.
incident_assignments — id, incident_id, assigned_to_user_id, assigned_team (operations/support/finance/supplier_manager), assigned_at.

