17. AI Engine Domain (D-005 — drafts only, never auto-publish)

ai_generation_logs — id, type (airport_description/seo_metadata/faq/schema/ai_summary/guide/service_explainer/internal_links), target_entity_type, target_entity_id, locale, model, prompt_version, prompt (text), output (jsonb), token_cost, status (generated/accepted/edited/rejected), reviewed_by, created_at.
