20. Key Relationships (ERD summary)

- airport 1—N airport_services N—1 service. airport_service is the central hub.
- airport_service 1—N pricing_rules, 1—N availability_rules, 1—N supplier_coverage.
- supplier N—N airport (via supplier_airports), N—N service (via supplier_services), N—N airport_service (via supplier_coverage).
- customer 1—N bookings. booking N—1 airport_service, booking N—1 supplier (nullable).
- booking 1—1 booking_price_snapshot, 1—N booking_passengers, 1—N booking_flights, 1—N booking_status_history, 1—N booking_supplier_assignments, 1—N booking_notes, 1—N booking_events.
- booking 1—N payments 1—N payment_transactions. booking 1—N refunds.
- settlement 1—N settlement_lines (each line N—1 booking). settlement 1—N payouts.
- incident N—1 booking (nullable), N—1 supplier (nullable).
- page 1—N page_translations, 1—N schema_blocks, N—N page (via internal_links).
- ai_generation_logs / translation_jobs → content_approval_workflow → published content.

